{"product_id": "39190", "page": 2, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-01-13", "text": "At first, I set lauch options and fixed some minor issues with the Steam version.  Lo and behold, the steam version deserves its poor reputation.  I just finished the game, not remembering it was the ending from when I competed it in 2003.  I didn't even get a chance to pick up the loot from the final boss, it just went immediately back to the game menu.  What a frusrating release.", "hours": 25.4, "user_id": "76561197968160389", "username": "bne5151457", "products": 63, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39190", "page": 2, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-01-12", "text": "Classic game, shame multiplayer is almost unworkable.\nWith multiplayer hobbled, and barely working via work arounds, the main of appeal of this game is gone. The single player mod is lonely and boring.\nI got it on sale, 0.99p so i do not feel too ripped off, but If I paid full price I would be disapointed.", "hours": 2.7, "user_id": "76561198312236680", "username": "alex1453ad", "products": 27, "early_access": false}
