{"product_id": "39190", "page": 5, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-11-30", "text": "I LOVE Dungeon Siege and will play the heck out of it!  However some of the things I love the most about it are NOT in the Steam version sadly.  LOA expansion is not available and multiplayer is disabled.  The multiplayer, especially, is why I bought this!  So I could play it with my sons and husband, like we used to... and we loved LOA.... who DOESN'T want the pimp hat and the eggchucking spell??  Awesomeness x 100!   If you have a way to play this with the actual game, with the expansion, do that.", "hours": 21.6, "user_id": "76561198448429886", "username": "juddstress", "products": 4, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
