{"product_id": "39190", "page": 14, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-06-24", "text": "Never knew what this was, got it pretty cheap and thought \"Eh might aswell try it.\" I absolutely love it, its great, even for such an old game where i have trouble keeping track of where i need to go, it entertained me highly. Sadly because there is some confusion about what i need to do and the rather repetitive gameplay i stopped playing and never actually finished the game. Still a good game though. Overall a good 7/10 I'd say.", "hours": 16.0, "username": "DVI", "products": 286, "early_access": false}
