{"product_id": "39190", "page": 20, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-25", "text": "I don't play a lot of games now a days. I believe although that I have scorned genres that could please me. This click-to-move-click-to-attack RPGs fall in those games. I loved torchlight 2 when i played it. And I this game resembles torchlight 2 a lot. However, it is PARTY-BASED-RPG, where you get to control multiple party members.\nAt the price this is available now(Dungeon Siege Collection, includes I, II and III), it is a must have, even if, like me, you dislike the genre.\nFor playtime, I have played this game for 8 hours in the first two days, which is kind of a lot for me nowadays.\nStrongly Recommended!", "hours": 8.8, "user_id": "76561198121375155", "username": "BOB_nachiketaom", "products": 1239, "early_access": false}
