{"product_id": "39190", "page": 22, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-25", "text": "This is perhaps one of all time favourite games, I got gifted the original CD copy which I still have as a child. The fun of exploring the world, with an interesting story, and there's an expansion although steam seems to have the legends of aranna which adds some of the most fun spells and funky gear.\nThere's plenty of characters you can have in a party, as the game gets progressivly harder for you, and making gold isn't always as easy as it seems.\nThe ambience, music and scenery may be dated to some, but to those that grew up with it then it's a welcome sight to see because the game itself has so much to offer", "hours": 2.8, "username": "Sam", "products": 1007, "early_access": false}
