{"product_id": "39190", "page": 23, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-23", "text": "Just a quick review for the Steam Award Nominations. This is my all-time favourite RPG. Great combat, a lot of variety, has mods and can be played online/in LAN. Beautiful soundtrack and modding adds a lot of playtime even if you can't easily find players to play with anymore. Graphics are still fine, but you'll need to tweak the settings quite a bit on newer operating systems and GPUS to be able to play.", "hours": 35.0, "username": "Nomine", "products": 1075, "early_access": false}
