{"product_id": "39190", "page": 24, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-10-28", "text": "This is one of the best classic adventure games i have played.\nIt features the classic way of intruduction to new creature, stronger one, Bossfight which leads to a bigger boss fight, though Gomm should have been a lot more difficult.\nUnfortunatly the steam version's Multiplayer is locked and it does not feature the legends of aranna expansion pack.\nWould be playing for a very long time to finish it.\nWould recommend having a fix for resolution and multiplayer.\nSpeechless of how steam treated this game.", "hours": 24.7, "username": "PsyCho_JL", "products": 49, "early_access": false}
