{"product_id": "39190", "page": 27, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-08-30", "text": "one of the best games ever - played it more than 1000h and loved LoA (Addon) (before steam - bought it again here)\nyou simply start to play and the actions you do decide what class your character will become\nso if you fight with Bow you become a Archer; if you fight with Sword u r a Warrior; if you do both you will be a ranger; you have 2 different kinds of magic what can be mixed in your build or maxed out as nature-magican or combat-sorcerer\ni would really enjoy a HD-remake with added features like craftsmanship, buying homes and maybe in a persistent multiplayer world (with private dedicated servers) -> would host a server and spend money on DLCs ;)", "hours": 4.8, "username": "aFF3_M!T_WaFF3", "products": 1308, "early_access": false}
