{"product_id": "39190", "page": 29, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-07", "text": "This game is my entire childhood. Played it non-stop with my brother and some friends in multiplayer... Imagine my disapointment when I found out that the steam edition doesn't have multiplayer.\nPros:\n- Music is perfect. Some of the best video game music ever made.\n- The atmosphere is very immersive and a real joy to rediscover.\n- Still packs a good challenge.\nCons:\n- Doesn't support today's typical resolutions.\n- Controls/Camera is little meh.\n(not too bad considering the original release date, but not up to par with today's standards)\n- NO MULTIPLAYER!", "hours": 11.1, "username": "Noodles", "products": 125, "early_access": false}
