{"product_id": "39190", "page": 38, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-13", "text": "Best to play this awesome classic via the exe, not via Steam.\nAlso remain in 1024x768.\nThis was my first arpg and from day one I was addicted to this masterpiece.\nA lot of management between the characters (armor & weapons) and you can even a pack animal with you to take more loot with your party.\nThe world is very big and with a lot of variation in flora, fauna and monsters.\nI completed it back then and now i wanna play at least to the swamp :)\nIs this a game for you? I don't know, but I can tell you for me personnaly I like this more than part 2 and 3 together !", "hours": 0.5, "user_id": "76561198079187939", "username": "DaisyInTheMiX", "products": 144, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
