{"product_id": "39190", "page": 42, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-07-04", "text": "Dungeon Siege was a great hack nslash dungeon crawler RPG when it was released and the mechanics are still solid even today, although the graphics have dated poorly.\nThe reason I do not recommend is that it is unplayable via steam and does not include the expansion pack Legends of Aranna.\nThere are a few guides that purport to help you run the game via the steam installation and although I've spent numerous hours following them to the \"T\" and reinstalling the game, it still does not work on Windows 8.1. (The hour I've spent \"playing\" was logging into the game on multiple occasions to see if it would work)\nIf possible try and get the original digital discs or make iso's of your original discs and play the game that way not via the steam copy.", "hours": 1.3, "username": "Deisophia", "products": 631, "early_access": false}
