{"product_id": "39190", "page": 43, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-24", "text": "**\nThe true meaning of hack n slash, x100.\nYou and a\n[not really] other people in your party just bash their weapons (or spam spells) into enemies while gaining loot Diablo style. You explore the vast land, killing every enemy on sight, and just lay hell upon them while spamming the H button. (Drink: Health Potion?)\nIf you want a game where you just go to town on every sorry enemy that happens to be in your party's vicinity and don't much care for a great story, you've come to the right place! Just don't forget to heal up everyone in your team! You'll regret what you'll see when they die.\nRecommended.", "hours": 14.1, "user_id": "76561198063651840", "username": "Naoto", "products": 312, "early_access": false}
