{"product_id": "39190", "page": 51, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-19", "text": "An awesome game that is missing from Steam. I have put many hundreds of hours into this game in the past. The copy that Steam sells DOES NOT WORK ON NEWER SYSTEMS. It is also missing the expansion: Legends of Aranna. The disc version works perfectly, even on newer systems. WTF STEAM. If you want to play this game, find disc packs instead of the Steam version, and I assure you that you'll have a much better time. This is a very fun game, but DO NOT BUY IT THROUGH STEAM.", "hours": 0.4, "username": "\u0e56\u06e3\u06dcKen\u2020eLL", "products": 457, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
