{"product_id": "39190", "page": 52, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-27", "text": "Dungeon Siege is exactly what the title says. You siege dungeons with a party.\nThis is one of my all time favorite games. Party based RPG. You can't go wrong with this one. Dungeon Siege has a fairly long story too. Hack and slash. There is combat magic nature magic and basic melee weaponry. Grab a pack mule and get ready for many many hours of dungeon crawling. A bit lacking in the class development but I have to say that is this games only down fall. Its wickedly fun!\n10/10 Would Siege Dungeon again.\nEdit: One minor grip its very very difficult to take screenshots. And prepare to die. Alot.", "hours": 44.5, "user_id": "76561198128263846", "username": "SirPugly", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
