{"product_id": "39190", "page": 57, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-01", "text": "I adore this game. My first Dungeone siege Game was Dungeon siege II and I can see similar gameplay when I play the first one. First time I played I could see where the second game got their mechanics and while this game has a more simplistic version of the second games levelling system I love it!! My first time playing I found it charming but as I contine to play the charm has turned into respect for the team that made the game and love for the game itself. I might be a little biased to my series as the dungeon sige series was one of my first RPG's but 10/10!!", "hours": 12.6, "user_id": "76561198150898638", "username": "River_C", "products": 125, "early_access": false}
