{"product_id": "39190", "page": 57, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-09-17", "text": "If you can get this game to run smoothly, so anything windows 7(in windows xp compatability mode) and lower, it's a good throw back even if the multiplayer has been removed. The combat in this game is epic, with anywhere from 1 enemy to 30 enemies in single battle not to mention your 7 other party members thrown into the frey. It fast passed early 2000's top down fantasy Diablo/Baudler's Gate style adventure role playing game with a bit more fluidity in its motions.  The only down side is it doesn't run on Windows 8", "hours": 0.2, "user_id": "76561198013491496", "username": "Parzival", "products": 78, "early_access": false}
