{"product_id": "39190", "page": 61, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-23", "text": "A great game and a wonderfull flash to the past. Nostalgia aside a very good game with awesome gameplay. With a range of different companions along with a purchable mule to slave around your gear. If you like RPG's or if you dont, do yourself a favor and go ahead and buy it.\n\u263cSteam usually does a goood job but they have yet to impress me as they have removed multiplayer along with the DLC\u263c\n~Multiplayer Fix - Launch Settings, type zonematch=true BAM DONE XD~", "hours": 5.4, "user_id": "76561198066982156", "username": "Captin Pickles", "products": 108, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39190", "page": 61, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-06-22", "text": "I love this game. Seriously, it's one of my all time favorites but I cannot recommend this to anyone who owns a Windows 8.1 computer and is feeling nostalgic to revisit this beautiful world again because you can't. It's not compatible with Windows 8.1 and I'm pretty upset that Steam didn't put a huge disclaimer in the product description about compatability issues because I just spent real money on a game that doesn't work.\nNOT HAPPY", "hours": 2.6, "username": "emannikcufesin", "products": 12, "early_access": false}
