{"product_id": "39190", "page": 70, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-10", "text": "I have loved this game since it came out. I have beaten it four times and know I will get the urge to play again. What separates this RPG is that you have more than one character to control. Bored of the Archer halfway through? Switch to the mage and control him. I love this game. Great for dungeon crawler fans!", "hours": 0.0, "user_id": "76561198045056306", "username": "Roland, Son of Steven", "products": 197, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39190", "page": 70, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-09-04", "text": "\"HOLY SH\u00cfT, this game is focking AMAZING!\" was pretty much my initial reaction to Dungeon Siege when my best friend showed it to me someteen years ago, and that reaction hasn't faded ever since. Dungeon Siege is to roleplaying/combat-adventure games as RoboCop is to, well... movies, basically. It took the world by storm, and sure, not many might acknowledge it these days, but it's still one of those permanent milestones which just smacked you raw with how great it was and still is, even compared to modern crap. Hell, even being threatened by two horribly sh\u00eftty excuses for sequels didn't ruin either of 'em. Hell naw! They just kept on truckin', and everybody with any brains knew this: the original one is the best one. 'Nuff said. 9.5/10", "hours": 0.0, "user_id": "76561198005079603", "username": "Captain Seasick", "products": 502, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39190", "page": 70, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2013-09-01", "text": "Dungeon Siege is one of my all-time favorites. I have some great memories attached to it, and so I can't really recommend you get it without cautioning that I am rather non-professional about it. HOWEVER\nDO NOT GET THIS VERSION OF THE GAME\nTHE MULTIPLAYER, AKA THE BEST PART, IS DISABLED. STAY AWAY! AWAY!\nYou can hack your way into it, but it's annoying and stupid.", "hours": 5.8, "username": "ReasonableSteve", "products": 1463, "early_access": false}
